Paul Harvey (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Harvey_(actor) 0 Paul Harvey (September 10, 1882 – December 5, 1955) was an American actor who appeared in at least 177 films. He is not to be confused with Paul Harvey the broadcaster. Paul_Harvey ( September_10_,_1882 – December_5_,_1955 ) was an_American_actor who appeared in at_least_177_films . He is not to_be_confused with Paul_Harvey the_broadcaster .
